Featuring 2 and 3 all en-suite bedroom apartments, Donyo Park is a thoughtfully designed residential development that incorporates the very best in architecture, internal finishes, and amenities coming up along Donyo Sabuk lane off General Mathenge Road in Nairobi’s Parklands/Westlands area. Also Read: 26 Mzizi Court Residences Development in Gigiri, Nairobi, Kenya Each of the apartments blends modern chic designs with open plan and contemporary spaces, large balconies, elegant European finishes incorporating stainless steel appliances, porcelain tiles, contemporary sanitary ware, and fitted designer kitchens.  Donyo Park Residents will be welcomed into a grand reception area with a lavish lobby, and a list of endless amenities ranging from a state of the art gym with steam rooms, resident’s lounge, and a rooftop barbeque area in addition to a rooftop party lawn with a breathtaking view of the Westlands area, an outdoor seating area, gazebos, a children’s playground, and a heated rooftop swimming pool. Other amenities include 3 high-speed elevators and an additional service elevator, multi-level car parks, and automatic power back up among others.  The project is developed by Elegant Properties Kenya, with Ethique Architects & Associates, and Amplus Consulting Engineers Limited as the architects and structural engineers respectively.